to take note of this.

238
00:17:42,300 --> 00:17:43,500
And so,

239
00:17:44,100 --> 00:17:46,367
today will be the last time

240
00:17:46,433 --> 00:17:49,600
you and I

241
00:17:50,767 --> 00:17:53,333
will meet.

242
00:17:55,600 --> 00:17:56,934
Please

243
00:17:58,633 --> 00:18:01,667
