Shall we?

303
00:21:47,266 --> 00:21:49,433
Of course. See you in a bit.

304
00:21:53,800 --> 00:21:56,967
Mr. Jeong, it's been a while.

305
00:21:57,033 --> 00:21:59,467
Yes, it has.

306
00:22:03,066 --> 00:22:04,600
Enjoy your time here.

307
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:53,467
