308
00:22:54,834 --> 00:22:57,100
Yes. Don't worry too much.

309
00:23:30,500 --> 00:23:31,667
Mom!

310
00:23:35,066 --> 00:23:36,266
Mom!

311
00:23:37,533 --> 00:23:38,700
Jae-heon.

312
00:23:39,834 --> 00:23:40,967
Jae-heon.

313
00:23:48,233 --> 00:23:49,300
Moon-seong.

314
00:23:52,433 --> 00:23:53,433
Moon-seong.

315
00:24:07,266 --> 00:24:08,600
Are you all right?

316
00:24:12,300 --> 00:24:13,567
Grandma.

317
00:24:13,633 --> 00:24:15,300
Oh, thank heavens.

318
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:18,033
Thank heavens you're okay.

319
00:24:20,300 --> 00:24:22,533
Oh, goodness.

320
00:24:23,667 --> 00:24:25,300
Thank heavens you're okay.

321
00:24:27,333 --> 00:24:29,934
Oh, what a relief.
I'm holding your soft hands.

322
00:24:30,533 --> 00:24:32,400
Grandma, I'm fine.

323
00:24:33,100 --> 00:24:36,066
Thank heavens. I thank the heavens.

324
00:24:37,600 --> 00:24:39,233
Thank you, Moon-seong.

325
00:24:41,467 --> 00:24:42,834
Thank you.

326
00:24:43,533 --> 00:24:44,967
Thank you.

327
00:24:49,700 --> 00:24:51,100
Moon-seong.

328
00:25:32,867 --> 00:25:34,834
Today was your greatest hurdle.

329
00:25:35,533 --> 00:25:37,400
Good job. You both did great.

330
00:25:37,467 --> 00:25:41,967
There won't be anything like this again,
so don't worry too much.

331
00:25:42,867 --> 00:25:44,066
Let's keep it going.

332
00:25:47,667 --> 00:25:48,667
Actually,

333
00:25:50,133 --> 00:25:51,734
