335
00:26:03,300 --> 00:26:04,467
The thing is,

336
00:26:06,266 --> 00:26:08,767
the more I become Ri Moon-seong,

337
00:26:08,834 --> 00:26:13,600
the more I feel like
I'm doing something wrong.

338
00:26:13,667 --> 00:26:15,100
