339
00:26:16,166 --> 00:26:17,633
This feels wrong.

340
00:26:19,333 --> 00:26:23,200
Do you feel like
you're doing something wrong?

341
00:26:27,533 --> 00:26:29,100
You've done nothing wrong.

342
00:26:30,166 --> 00:26:33,734
We're on a contractual agreement,
and you did as I asked.

343
00:26:34,300 --> 00:26:36,767
If what we're doing is wrong,

344
00:26:37,533 --> 00:26:38,900
